{"tid":1873635,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［不用識chem］自製次氯酸","createTime":"2020-02-10T18:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T05:10:23.000Z","uid":300855,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f43fe1284020b662d8b05b453fed08c300bc302c","tid":1873635,"uid":300855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:18:03.000Z","msg":"全方位抗菌液是利用次氯酸的強氧化力，瞬間產生殺菌效果。因次氯酸的氧化過程中，會與有機物快速結合，當次氯酸與細菌、病毒接觸後，次氯酸會與細菌、病毒的細胞膜結合，使細胞膜的結構產生變化，使細菌、病毒無法存活而產生殺菌效果。<br />\n<br />\n基於出面啲酒精同次氯酸都炒到勁貴<br />\n所以大家可以加醋去漂白水生成cl2<br />\n再加cl2去h2o生成次氯酸<br />\n咁大家就唔會死於肺炎<br />\n利申： chem2<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我喺網上面搵到生成器,售價約3xx-1xxx不等<br />\n但好處係可以長期使用,以及大量生產<br />\n市面上嘅次氯酸水賣$79/100mL<br />\n自製cp值高好多<br />\n有多仲可以送俾親朋戚友<br />\n唔似送口罩咁肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/frmB3TF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfrmB3TF.png&h=fdc59e75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫師指出,次氯酸水是透過電解食鹽而得出的產物，刺激性較低。<br />\n<br />\n透過電解原理, 產生的活性氧離子, 有效殺菌99.98%<br />\n電解後會產生功能水H2O, 活性氧, 氧化劑和次氯酸, 次氯酸的殺菌能力是漂白水的80倍<br />\n<br />\n簡單而言原理係透過電解出次氯酸<br />\n而保存方法就係用amber bottle<br />\n<br />\n次氯酸水入面主要殺菌成分為次氯酸，接觸紫外線或有機物即於短時間內發揮氧化作用後分解還原為水。由於生成機所產出的殺菌水為即產即用，故無需顧慮保存期限問題。至於瓶裝抗菌噴霧或補充桶，在常溫、遮光及瓶口緊閉狀態下，可保存6~9個月。至餘已填充入霧化器中之殺菌水，建議應於一周內使用完畢。<br />\n<br />\n大家如果覺得有用就幫我推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇用就隨佢沉"},{"pid":"de916dff321367ae33dffa50cc246f0850a6e310","tid":1873635,"uid":61918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:28:34.000Z","msg":"好似好複雜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b055db1fa3517ab423e5c6a04d0b1a1952e340","tid":1873635,"uid":300855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de916dff321367ae33dffa50cc246f0850a6e310","tid":1873635,"uid":61918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:28:34.000Z","msg":"好似好複雜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:31:52.000Z","msg":"水加鹽only<br />\n上面派膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42025511179ddc591e3e3ecdf6b59d9bd04ce16","tid":1873635,"uid":42250,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:32:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚信佢<br />\n醋加漂白水出氯氣, 一戰殺人毒氣<br />\n唔死都會聞到肺氣腫</span>"},{"pid":"7834f967fa11ffb477be422d9ab6def289a91b24","tid":1873635,"uid":300855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a42025511179ddc591e3e3ecdf6b59d9bd04ce16","tid":1873635,"uid":42250,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:32:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚信佢<br />\n醋加漂白水出氯氣, 一戰殺人毒氣<br />\n唔死都會聞到肺氣腫</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:32:38.000Z","msg":"Sorry下面先正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7777f278d01fed1145c27ba24114ca64c69d3a","tid":1873635,"uid":204213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T19:21:12.000Z","msg":"電解鹽水都係會出氯氣咖喎...點自製呀..."},{"pid":"9834213c67a7ae7c6795ba66d70aa8114c6961e2","tid":1873635,"uid":300855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb7777f278d01fed1145c27ba24114ca64c69d3a","tid":1873635,"uid":204213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T19:21:12.000Z","msg":"電解鹽水都係會出氯氣咖喎...點自製呀..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"部機製<br />\n不是人手製<br />\n上面人手製純粹派膠<br />\n<br />\n電解後會產生功能水H2O, 活性氧, 氧化劑和次氯酸, 次氯酸的殺菌能力是漂白水的80倍<br />\n而且適合家居使用丶可消毒嬰兒用品<br />\n<br />\n可能我1999<br />\n但啱先search到台灣已經有人做緊"}]}